# Per-Dockerfile ignore (BuildKit) — paths relative to the build context root
# (the workspace dir holding kai-cli/ kai-core/ kai-engine/). The Dockerfile
# COPYs only those three module dirs, so just prune heavy siblings + non-source
# weight from the context upload. (No `*` whitelist — it can strip the local
# module contents and make the replace/workspace build fetch the pinned tag.)
kai-tui/
kai-server/
old-kai/
bench/
**/.git
**/node_modules
**/testdata
